            <div type="edition" xml:lang="tam-Latn" rendition="class:tamil maturity:vernacular">
                <ab>
                    <lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">śubham astu svasti</hi>
                </ab>                
                <p>
                    śrīmaN mahā-rājādirāja-rāja parameśvara rāyara kaṇṭa <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> daka śrī rāya maṉō payaṅkara bhāṣaikku-t tappuva rāyara kaṇṭa
                    <lb n="2" break="no"/>śvara veṉṟa <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> stāpaṉācāriya gaja-vēṭṭai śrī-vīra-pratāpa śrī-vīra-catāśiva-tēva makā-rāyar prutivi-rājyam paṇṇi Aruḷā niṉṟa cakābtam 1000 4 100 8 10 1 ṉ mēl cellā niṉṟa cittārtti samvatsarattu tulā ṉāyaṟṟu Aparapakṣattu pañcami
                    <lb n="3"/>caṉi-vāramum peṟṟa puṉar pūca na<hi rend="grantha">kṣa<supplied reason="omitted">tra</supplied></hi>t=tu nāḷ ceyaṅ-koṇṭa-cōḻa-maṇṭalattu cantirakiri-rājyattu <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> kōṭṭattu nakaraṅ kāñcipuram tiru-vekā nayiṉār kōyil śrī-paṇṭārattārōm śrī-perum-pūtūr Etirāciyaṟku cilācāsanam
                    <lb n="4"/>paṇṇi-k kuṭutta paṭi ṉāṅkaḷ muṉṉāḻikku Uḻavaṭai kāṇippaṭi śāsanam paṇṇi-k kuṭutta Ik-kārayaṉ tōppu meṭṭu <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> maṉai-p-piṟakkaṭaikku teṟku rāmarācar tōṭṭattukku mēṟku ṉātar taricukku teṉ kiḻakku tama
                    <lb n="5"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="8" unit="character"/> ṣa payat te <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> nilamāṉa Akkiṟāra <gap reason="lost" quantity="29" unit="character"/>
                    <lb n="6"/>tōppu tiru-vekā nayiṉār <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> samaṟpikkaiyil Inta tōppu nilamāṉa <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> vaiccu teṉṉa maram māvaṭai maravaṭai payirātti maṇṭapamum taṭi Ira
                    <lb n="7" break="no"/>vāl vīccu vaṭakku tattaricaṉivākuṭi ṉūṟṟu muppatum maṭam nīkki ka <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> koṇṭu namakku śiṣyar Āka naṭatta-k kaṭavōm ākavum Emperumāṉ <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> Eḻunt-aruḷi maṇṭapattilē Amutu ceyt-aruḷa poliyūṭṭu-k kaṭṭiṉatukku vi <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> tiru-vekā nayiṉā
                    <!--Lines 8-13 are longer!-->
                    <lb n="8"/>tiru-vāṉi-t-tiru-ṉāḷukku mūṉṟān tiru-ṉāḷukku maṇṭapattilē Eḻunt-aruḷi Amutu ceyt-aruḷa poliyūṭṭu-k
                    <lb n="9"/>ṅa ney Uri cīrakam sarkkarai <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> yaṟṟan tiru-p paṇiyārattukku payaṟu<gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/>vaṅa vellam
                    <lb n="10"/>Ōṇa <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> tiruṉāḷukku perumāḷ Eḻuntaruḷi Amutu ceytaruḷum Appa paṭi ka kku
                    <lb n="11"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> U vaṅa tayir vaṅa kkum <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> Amutu sa <gap reason="lost" quantity="13" unit="character"/> Amutupaṭi
                    <lb n="12"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> payaṟṟam tiru-p-paṇiyārattukku payaṟu vellam līṭa pāṉakattukku vellam
                    <lb n="13"/>tta pu tiru-p-pāṭi vēṭṭai kaṇṭaruḷa perumāḷ tirumpa Eḻuntaruḷkaiyil maṇṭapattil Amutu ceytaruḷa Appam <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> ku Amutupaṭi <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/>
                    <!--There are 6 more lines! Or is it another inscription?-->
                    <!--There are more blocks engraved on the right. Or is it another inscription?-->
